298
00:13:09.489 --> 00:13:10.590
boogity, boogity, boogity.

299
00:13:10.657 --> 00:13:15.262
<i>♪</i>

300
00:13:15.328 --> 00:13:18.165
<i>[somber guitar music]</i>

301
00:13:18.231 --> 00:13:20.100
<i>There was no way that June</i>

302
00:13:20.167 --> 00:13:22.135
<i>was not gonna be
front and center.</i>

303
00:13:22.202 --> 00:13:23.904
<i>It's hard for her
to stand still</i>

304
00:13:23.971 --> 00:13:28.008
and not interject.
[laughs]

305
00:13:28.075 --> 00:13:35.215
<i>♪</i>

306
00:13:36.884 --> 00:13:40.988
<i>We had come to Nashville,
