419
00:18:29.442 --> 00:18:32.479
<i>and songs and routines</i>

420
00:18:32.545 --> 00:18:36.216
that she had honed
over decades.

421
00:18:36.283 --> 00:18:37.717
Miss June Carter.

422
00:18:37.784 --> 00:18:40.753
[cheers and applause]

423
00:18:40.820 --> 00:18:44.924
<i>Nashville at the time
was stuck in this image</i>

424
00:18:44.991 --> 00:18:48.995
of the little homemaker.

425
00:18:49.061 --> 00:18:52.765
<i>The "Opry" was insistent
that women should dress</i>

426
00:18:52.832 --> 00:18:55.168
in those kind of
gingham checks

427
00:18:55.235 --> 00:18:57.670
and be very conservative.

428
00:18:57.737 --> 00:18:59.806
I'm getting
a cold in my nose.

429
00:18:59.872 --> 00:19:04.177
Life gets tedious, don't it?

430
00:19:04.244 --> 00:19:07.180
[applause]

431
00:19:12.285 --> 00:19:13.786
<i>[light guitar music]</i>

432
00:19:13.853 --> 00:19:15.255
<i>There was a difficult time
