440
00:19:41.080 --> 00:19:42.682
<i>and she could still
go play the "Opry,"</i>

441
00:19:42.749 --> 00:19:45.552
<i>but he didn't think
she'd be out on the road.</i>

442
00:19:45.618 --> 00:19:48.488
And Mama always said
that she was covered up

443
00:19:48.555 --> 00:19:50.723
with ambition,
that she was absolutely

444
00:19:50.790 --> 00:19:52.625
<i>filled with ambition.</i>

445
00:19:52.692 --> 00:19:55.862
<i>She had all these things
she wanted to do.</i>

446
00:19:55.928 --> 00:19:57.730
<i>I think she wanted to be--</i>

447
00:19:57.797 --> 00:19:59.632
I think she just wanted
to be a superstar.

448
00:19:59.699 --> 00:20:02.802
<i>♪</i>

449
00:20:02.869 --> 00:20:06.406
<i>I detected a little sarcasm
in that voice</i>

450
00:20:06.473 --> 00:20:07.740
<i>when I heard you
putting me on.</i>

451
00:20:07.807 --> 00:20:09.376
I said, "What's the matter
